title: Southeast Florida Transportation Council Peer Review
text: Transportation Research Board > Blurbs > Southeast Florida Transportation Council Peer Review Text Size: Southeast Florida Transportation Council Peer Review http://www.fhwa.dot.gov/planning/tmip/resources/peer_review_program/seftc/fhwahep15060.pdf 173339 Southeast Florida Transportation Council Peer Review The U.S. Federal Highway Administration has released a report that details a peer review of the Southeast Florida Transportation Council’s (SEFTC) transportation model, which is intended to aid SEFTC with its new regional travel model and to guide its data collection activities.
